g mit den Spielfilmen und den historischen Ereignissen werden zudem einige zentrale Fragen der Holocaust-Forschung behandelt: Fragen nach der Definition des Widerstands, Fragen nach Leben und Überleben, der Ethik der Rache und schließlich: Inwieweit können wir diesen Ereignissen mit moralischen Kategorien begegnen?  aThe focus of this volume is on the reception and representation of Jewish resistance and the relationship between historiography and film fiction during the Holocaust. Three American feature films are examined from the perspectives of history and film science. The central question is: Can film fiction provide relevant historiographic understanding?  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 4aAuschwitz (Auschwitz-Birkenau). 4aHolocaust. 4aJüdischer Widerstand. 4aWarschauer Ghetto. 7aHISTORY / Jewish.2bisacsh  aAuschwitz (Auschwitz-Birkenau).  aHolocaust.  aJewish resistance.  aWarsaw Ghetto.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2019z978311071956708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2019z9783110606195oZDB-23-DEG0 cEPUBz97831106021350 cprintz978311060178740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311060472640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110604726423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110604726.jpg  a978-3-11-071956-7  DG Plus eBook-Package 2019b2019  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2019  aZDB-23-DGGb2019